{"type":"article","id":10685,"title":"民族、族群概念以及汉人族群概念","uid":21662,"topics":[462,4029],"contents":"一个民族或种族是谁的人类别<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Identity_(social_science)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">标识</a>彼此，通常在一个假定的共同家谱或血统的基础上或相似之处，如常见的<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Language\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">语言</a>或<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dialect\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">方言</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/History\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">历史</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Society\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">社会</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Culture\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">文化</a>或<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nation\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">民族</a>。种族经常与“<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nation\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">民族</a>”一词同义，尤其是在<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ethnic_nationalism\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">种族民族主义的</a>情况下，它与<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Race_(human_categorization)\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">种族</a>概念是分离的但又相关。<br>\n<br>\n种族通常是基于一个人所生活的社会的继承地位。一个民族的成员往往是由共同的<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cultural_heritage\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">文化遗产</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ancestry\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">血统</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Origin_myth\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">起源神话</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/History\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">历史</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Homeland\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">祖国</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Language\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">语言</a>或<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Dialect\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">方言</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Religion\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">宗教</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mythology\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">神话</a>和<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ritual\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">仪式</a>等符号系统，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Cuisine\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">美食</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Folk_costume\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">着装风格</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Art\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">艺术</a>或<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Human_physical_appearance\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">外观来定义的</a>。种族群体经常继续说<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Language_family\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">相关语言，</a>并共享相似的<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Gene_pool\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">基因库</a>。通过<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Language_shift\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">语言转换</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Acculturation\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">适应</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Adoption\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">采用</a>和<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Religious_conversion\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">宗教信仰转换</a>，有时个人或团体可以离开一个民族而成为另一个民族的一部分（除了强调<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Homogeneity_and_heterogeneity\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">同质性</a>或<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Racial_hygiene\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">种族纯洁</a>作为主要成员资格标准的民族之外）。<br>\n<br>\n在现代，最大的族群由亿万个民族组成（<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Han_Chinese\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">汉族</a>是最大的族群），而最小的<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indigenous_peoples\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">族裔</a>则仅限于几十个个体（全世界有许多<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Indigenous_peoples\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">土著人民</a>）。族群可以细分为亚族或<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tribe\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">部落</a>，随着时间的流逝，由于<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Endogamy\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">内婚配偶</a>或与父母群体的<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Geographical_segregation\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">隔离</a>，这些族群本身可能会成为独立的族群。相反，以前分开的种族可以合并形成一个<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pan-ethnicity\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">全种族</a>（例如<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Han_Chinese\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">汉族</a>），并最终可能<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Melting_pot\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">合并为一个种族</a>。无论是通过分裂还是通过合并，形成独立的种族身份被称为<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ethnogenesis\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">民族发生</a>。<br>\n汉族概念<br>\n汉祖，汉族人（<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/British_English\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">UK</a>：<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA/English\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">/ ħ æ Ñ /</a>;<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/American_English\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">美国</a>：<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Help:IPA/English\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">/ ^ h ɑː ñ /</a>;<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Simplified_Chinese_characters\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">简化中国</a>：汉人;<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Traditional_Chinese_characters\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">中国传统</a>：汉人;<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Pinyin\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">拼音</a>：Hànrén;从字面上：'啥人'&nbsp;或简化中国：汉族;繁体中文：汉族;拼音：Hànzú;字面意思：“汉族”），是一个<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/East_Asian_people\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">东亚</a><a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ethnic_group\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">族群</a>和<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nation\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">国家</a>原产于中国。他们构成了<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/List_of_contemporary_ethnic_groups\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">世界上最大的族裔</a>，约占<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/World_population\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">全球人口的</a>18％。估计有13亿汉族人主要集中在<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Mainland_China\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">中国大陆</a>（约占总人口的91.6％）。在<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Taiwan\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">台湾</a>他们约占人口的95％。汉族血统的人也占<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Singapore\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新加坡</a>总人口的75％左右。<br>\n<br>\n汉人的历史可以追溯到<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Huaxia\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">华夏（Huaxia）</a>，<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Huaxia\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">华夏</a>是<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Yellow_River\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">黄河沿岸</a>最初的农业部落联盟的名称。华夏一词代表<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zhongyuan\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">华北地区</a>农业部落华夏的<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Neolithic\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">新石器时代</a>联合会，他们定居在中国北方黄河中下游附近的<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Zhongyuan\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">中原</a>地区。这两个部落是现代汉人的祖先，汉人诞生了中华文明。另外，术语华夏（字面上的“文明的夏族”）被用来代表一个文明的种族群体，与周围的<a href=\"https://en.m.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hua-Yi_distinction\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\">野蛮人</a>形成鲜明对比。","date":"2019-12-09","agreeCount":0,"discussionCount":0}